title.rendered: Eric Dane, Rebecca Gayheart Welcome Baby Girl!

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

McSteamy is now McDaddy. Eric Dane and his wife, Rebecca Gayheart, are new parents to a baby girl. The little cutie is the couple’s first child together!

The couple’s daughter arrived on Wednesday in Los Angeles, the couple’s rep Nanci Ryder said. “Mother, father and daughter are doing great,” said Ryder.

A name has not yet been released, but the Grey’s Anatomy star had previously said Gayheart wanted to meet the baby before making a final decision.

“I’m really excited,” Dane told Ellen DeGeneres in an interview airing last month. “I’m just going to stay close to my wife and make sure she is all right.”

A pair of proud, attractive parents.

Dane and Gayheart, who wed in Vegas in 2004, revealed they were having a girl in December, just a few months after the Eric Dane nude tape release.

Congratulations to the happy couple!
